If you want to translate NexSession, you're welcome !

    go to ./locale : 
        cd locale
        
    copy file nexsession_en_US.ts to nexsession_xx_XX.ts
    replace xx and XX with the letters of your language.
        cp nexsession_en_US.ts nexsession_xx_XX.ts
        
    open your .ts file with QLinguist, make your translations and publish.

    
in order to try it:
    go to parent dir:
        cd ..
        
    open Makefile in a text editor
    add nexsession_xx_XX.qm to the Makefile (line 42)
    save Makefile
    
    then make:
        make


    
    




